{"tid":1635644,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣同我入黎睇","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:32:51.000Z","uid":299716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b9fbd58d58353a72da53782228420321001136","tid":1635644,"uid":299716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:27:58.000Z","msg":"屋企個黃絲奶今日收到呢張文宣想同各位文宣大佬講幾句：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 啲字唔該大隻啲</span><br />\n<br />\n啲上咗年紀既睇唔到咁細隻字，大隻小小，當做presentation咁design。啲無知師奶只會比雞乸咁大隻字吸引<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.寫重點</span><br />\n<br />\n無知師奶唔會同你睇過程/條例內容細節，直接講會導致咩結啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.吸引讀者障眼法</span><br />\n<br />\n如下圖文宣，一開始就甚麼是《禁蒙面法》，黃絲奶建議用「政府呼籲支持蒙面法」，等無知師奶/藍絲以為係政府文宣，從而有讀落去既動力<br />\n<br />\n最後，真係唔係插做文宣既各位大佬，好多謝你地既付出，只係希望討論一下文宣仲有咩改善空間，達至更佳成效<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKUU3qV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKUU3qV.jpg&h=c610ff2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwNSP5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwNSP5i.jpg&h=9aaad9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n解散狗隊，刻不容緩<br />\n六大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecc8db9826524268d0a229e0e1f4d4c7b8394638","tid":1635644,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"}]}